name: Community analysis and feeding ecology of the ichthyofauna in Gazi Bay sampled in August 1993
description: Counts of observed fish species and numericalandgravimetrical stomach analysis for 9fish species at the West andEast creek of Gazi Bay during a 2 day sampling in August 1993. The datawere digitized by VLIZ from the originalreport: De Troch, M. (1995).
